Ghana nye [[Afrika]] dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] lɔƒo. Ghana do liƒo kple [[Togo]] kple , [[Côte d'Ivoire]] kpakple [[Burkina Faso]]. Aƒu si woyɔna be ''[[Gulf of Guinea]]'' la le eƒe anyiehe lɔƒo. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 22,113,000 lɔƒo.
Woɖo Ghana tso ''Gold Coast'' kpakple ''British Togoland'' si nɔ Fransetɔwo ƒe dziɖuɖu te la ƒe kpekpe me. Ghana dukɔa xɔ dokuisinɔnɔ tso Eŋlisiawo gbɔ le Tedoxe 6 dzi, le ƒe 1957 me. Ghana ƒe fiadzue nye [[Accra]].

== Dukplɔlawo ==

Ghana ƒe dukplɔla enye [[John Dramani Mahama]]. Ele dziɖum tso Dzome 7, 2012. Eƒe kpeɖeŋutɔ enye Amissah Arthur.

